trans-unit.source: Represents a window that supports content navigation.
trans-unit.target: 콘텐츠 탐색을 지 원하는 창을 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: NavigationWindow derives from <xref:System.Windows.Window> and extends it with the ability to navigate to and display content.
trans-unit.target: 파생 된 NavigationWindow <xref:System.Windows.Window>탐색 하 고 콘텐츠를 표시 하는 기능을 사용 하도록 확장 합니다.</xref:System.Windows.Window>

trans-unit.source: Content can be any [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winfx](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winfx-md.md)] object or [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_html](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-html-md.md)] file.
trans-unit.target: 콘텐츠 하나가 될 수 있습니다 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winfx](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winfx-md.md)] 개체 또는 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_html](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-html-md.md)] 파일입니다.

trans-unit.source: In general, however, a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Page> object is the preferred way to package content for navigation.
trans-unit.target: 그러나, 일반적으로 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Page>개체를 사용 하 여 콘텐츠를 탐색 합니다.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Page>

trans-unit.source: Content can be navigated to by setting the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Source%2A> property with the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] for the desired content.
trans-unit.target: 설정 하 여 콘텐츠를 탐색할 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Source%2A>된 속성의 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] 원하는 콘텐츠에 대 한.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Source%2A>

trans-unit.source: Additionally, content can be navigated to by using one of the following overloads of the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A> method: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.Object%29> When content is navigated to by [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)], NavigationWindow will return an object that contains the content.
trans-unit.target: 또한 콘텐츠 탐색할 수 있습니다 다음 오버 로드 중 하나를 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A>메서드:- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Uri%29>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.Object%29>하 여 콘텐츠를 탐색 하는 경우 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)], NavigationWindow에 콘텐츠를 포함 하는 개체가 반환 됩니다.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.Object%29> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Navigation by [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] also supports navigation to a content fragment.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > 탐색 하 여 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] 도 콘텐츠 조각 탐색을 지원 합니다.

trans-unit.source: See <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.FragmentNavigation>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.FragmentNavigation>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.FragmentNavigation> 를 참조 하십시오.

trans-unit.source: Alternatively, content can be navigated to by using one of the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A> method overloads that accepts an object: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Object%29> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Object%2CSystem.Object%29> The lifetime of a navigation can be tracked through the following events: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigating> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigated> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationProgress> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationFailed> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationStopped> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.LoadCompleted> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.FragmentNavigation>.
trans-unit.target: 또는 콘텐츠 탐색할 수 있습니다 중 하나를 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A>메서드 오버 로드는 개체를 받아들이는:- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Object%29>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Object%2CSystem.Object%29>다음 이벤트를 통해 탐색 수명을 추적할 수 있습니다:- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigating>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigated>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationProgress>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationFailed>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationStopped>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.LoadCompleted>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.FragmentNavigation>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.FragmentNavigation> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.LoadCompleted> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationStopped> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationFailed> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationProgress> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigated> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigating> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Object%2CSystem.Object%29> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Object%29> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A>

trans-unit.source: Not all events are raised each time that a navigation occurs; the set of events that are raised is determined by the type of navigation that occurs (content or content fragment) and how the navigation completes (canceled, stopped, or failed).
trans-unit.target: 일부 이벤트가 발생 될 때마다 탐색에는 다음이 발생 합니다. 발생 하는 이벤트 집합이 (취소, 중지, 또는 실패) 형식 (콘텐츠 또는 콘텐츠 조각) 발생 하는 탐색 및 탐색이 완료 되는 방식에 따라 결정 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: The following figure illustrates the sequence in which these events will fire: ![Page navigation flow chart](~/add/media/navigationoverviewfigure11.png "Page navigation flow chart") During or after a navigation, NavigationWindow provides information about the content that is being navigated to, including the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the content being navigated to (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Source%2A>), the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the current content (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CurrentSource%2A>), and an object that contains the content that was navigated to (<xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A>).
trans-unit.target: 다음 그림은 이러한 이벤트는 발생 순서: ![페이지 탐색 흐름 차트](~/add/media/navigationoverviewfigure11.png "페이지 탐색 흐름 차트") NavigationWindow 되 고 탐색을 포함 하 여 콘텐츠에 대 한 정보를 제공 하는 동안 또는 탐색 후의 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] 탐색 중인 콘텐츠에의 (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Source%2A>), [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] 현재 콘텐츠의 (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CurrentSource%2A>), 및 탐색 하는 콘텐츠를 포함 하는 개체 (<xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CurrentSource%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Source%2A>

trans-unit.source: When content is navigated to, NavigationWindow records the navigation as an entry in navigation history.
trans-unit.target: 콘텐츠 탐색 NavigationWindow 탐색 기록의 항목으로 탐색을 기록 합니다.

trans-unit.source: An entry is added to back navigation history when either a new navigation occurs, by calling the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A> method, or by navigating to an entry in forward navigation history, by calling <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 호출 하 여 새 탐색 발생 될 때 탐색 기록을 다시에 항목이 추가 되는 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A>메서드, 또는 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A> 를 호출 하 여 앞으로 탐색 기록의 항목으로 이동 하 여</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A>

trans-unit.source: An entry is added to forward navigation history by navigating to an entry in back navigation history, by calling <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 항목 기록에 추가 됩니다 앞으로 탐색 뒤에 항목으로 이동 하 여 탐색 기록은 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A> 를 호출 하 여

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CanGoBack%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CanGoForward%2A> report whether there are entries in back and forward navigation history, respectively.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CanGoBack%2A>및 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CanGoForward%2A>있는지 여부를 보고 하 고 앞으로 탐색 기록 항목 뒤에 각각.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CanGoForward%2A></xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CanGoBack%2A>

trans-unit.source: The first time that one piece of content is navigated to from another piece of content, NavigationWindow automatically displays a navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] that allows users to navigate back and forwards through navigation history.
trans-unit.target: 처음으로의 콘텐츠는 한 부분을 탐색 하는 콘텐츠의 다른 부분에서 NavigationWindow 탐색을 자동으로 표시 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] 사용자가 다시 이동할 수 있도록 하 고 탐색 기록을 통해 전달 합니다.

trans-unit.source: You can configure when the navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] is shown by setting the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ShowsNavigationUI%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 시점을 구성할 수는 탐색 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] 설정 하 여 표시 되는 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ShowsNavigationUI%2A>속성.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ShowsNavigationUI%2A>

trans-unit.source: The most recent entry in back navigation history can be removed by calling <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 뒤로 탐색 기록의 가장 최근 항목 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A> 를 호출 하 여 제거할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: NavigationWindow does not store an instance of a content object in navigation history.
trans-unit.target: NavigationWindow 탐색 기록의 콘텐츠 개체의 인스턴스를 저장 하지 않습니다.

trans-unit.source: Instead, NavigationWindow creates a new instance of the content object each time it is navigated to by using navigation history.
trans-unit.target: 대신, NavigationWindow 탐색 기록을 사용 하 여 탐색할 될 때마다 콘텐츠 개체의 새 인스턴스를 만듭니다.

trans-unit.source: This behavior is designed to avoid excessive memory consumption when large numbers and large pieces of content are being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: 이 문제는 많은 수 및 대규모 콘텐츠를 탐색할 때 과도 한 메모리 소비를 방지 하도록 설계 되었습니다.

trans-unit.source: Consequently, the state of the content is not remembered from one navigation to the next.
trans-unit.target: 따라서 콘텐츠 상태는 다음 탐색에서 저장 되지 않습니다.

trans-unit.source: However, [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] provides several techniques by which you can store a piece of state for a piece of content in navigation history.
trans-unit.target: 그러나 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] 탐색 기록의 콘텐츠의 부분에 대 한 상태를 저장할 수 있는 몇 가지 방법을 제공 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Using <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>, you can also remember multiple sets of state for a single page instance.
trans-unit.target: 사용 하 여 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>, 여러 인스턴스를 단일 페이지에 대 한 상태 집합을 기억할 수도 있습니다.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>

trans-unit.source: NavigationWindow is one of two navigators in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], the other being <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>.
trans-unit.target: NavigationWindow의 두 탐색기 중 하나는 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], 다른 되 고 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>

trans-unit.source: Essentially, navigator is a class supports navigation and navigation history.
trans-unit.target: 기본적으로, 탐색기 탐색 및 탐색 기록을 지 원하는 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: Visually, [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)] use [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)] as a navigator, to provide an integrated user experience.
trans-unit.target: 시각적으로 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)] 사용 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)] 통합 된 사용자 환경을 제공할 수 있도록을 탐색기로 합니다.

trans-unit.source: However, [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)] actually use NavigationWindow as the navigator; the <xref:System.Windows.Application.MainWindow%2A> property of an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] running in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)] will return a reference to the NavigationWindow, and the navigation history that is managed by the NavigationWindow is integrated with the navigation history that is managed by [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 그러나 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)] 실제로 NavigationWindow를 탐색기;로 사용 하는 <xref:System.Windows.Application.MainWindow%2A>속성의는 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] 에서 실행 중인 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)] 의 NavigationWindow에 대 한 참조 반환 하 고 탐색 기록의 NavigationWindow가 관리 하는 탐색 기록에서 관리 되는 통합 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)].</xref:System.Windows.Application.MainWindow%2A>

trans-unit.source: **Content Model:** NavigationWindow is a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl>, which means that NavigationWindow can contain content such as text, images, or panels.
trans-unit.target: **콘텐츠 모델:** NavigationWindow가는 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl>, 즉, NavigationWindow가 같은 텍스트, 이미지 또는 패널 콘텐츠를 포함할 수 있습니다.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl>

trans-unit.source: Also, NavigationWindow is a root element and, consequently, cannot be part of another element's content.
trans-unit.target: 또한 NavigationWindow는 루트 요소 이며, 결과적으로, 다른 요소 내용이 포함 될 수 없습니다.
